OL,3,CFormer Wales winger Leighton James
OL,4,Cdies aged 71
OL,6,FFormer Wales winger Leighton James has
OL,7,Fdied at the age of 71.
OL,9,FJames won 54 caps for Wales and scored
OL,10,F10 goals, including a penalty to
OL,11,Fsecure victory over England at Wembley
OL,12,Fin 1977.
OL,14,FThe winger started his career at
OL,15,FBurnley and would also turn out for
OL,16,FDerby County and Sunderland.
