OL,4,Cdies aged 71
OL,6,FThe Football Association of Wales said
OL,7,Fon X, formerly Twitter: "It is with
OL,8,Fgreat sadness that we share the news
OL,9,Fthat Cymru international Leighton
OL,10,FJames has sadly passed away.J"James
OL,11,Fwas capped 54 times and scored 10
OL,12,Fgoals for Cymru. Amongst his most
OL,13,Ffamous moments with the dragon on his
OL,14,Fshirt was scoring a penalty in a
OL,15,Ffamous win over England at Wembley in
OL,16,F1977."J"He was a star of the only
OL,17,FCymru team to top a qualifying group
OL,18,Fbefore going on to reach the quarter-
OL,19,Ffinals of Euro 1976...
