OL,6,F"Our thoughts are with his family and
OL,7,Ffriends at this sad time."JSwansea
OL,8,FCity said they were "deeply saddened"
OL,9,Fby the news of James' passing in a
OL,10,Fstatement.
OL,12,F"The thoughts of everyone at Swansea
OL,13,FCity are with Leighton's friends and
OL,14,Ffamily at this sad time," the
OL,15,Fstatement read.
OL,17,F"Swansea City will wear black armbands
OL,18,Fin Saturday's Championship fixture
OL,19,Fagainst Huddersfield Town as a mark of
OL,20,Frespect.
