OL,6,F"Swansea City Under-21s will also wear
OL,7,Fblack armbands in their home match
OL,8,Fagainst Bristol City on Saturday."
OL,10,FThe rugby club in his hometown,
OL,11,FGorseinon RFC, described him on X,
OL,12,Fformerly Twitter, as "a top quality
OL,13,Fsportsman", while adding that
OL,14,F"Leighton was a true friend of the
OL,15,Fclub and will be sadly missed by our
OL,16,Fmembers past and present.
OL,18,F"Our thoughts are with his family at
OL,19,Fthis time."
