OL,4,Cdies aged 71
OL,6,FJames also played for Newport County,
OL,7,Fbut made his name at Burnley. In total
OL,8,Fhe played over 600 games in the
OL,9,FEnglish Football League.
OL,11,FHe also managed several teams in
OL,12,FWales, including Llanelli and Garden
OL,13,FVillage.
OL,15,FAnother of his former clubs, Newport
OL,16,FCounty, said the club's thoughts are
OL,17,Fwith his family.
