OL,3,CFormer Wales winger Leighton James
OL,4,Cdies aged 71
OL,6,FOn Friday evening after the news was
OL,7,Fannounced, Plaid Cymru leader Rhun ap
OL,8,FIorwerth described him as "One of the
OL,9,Fvery best. A true star and servant of
OL,10,FCymru football".
OL,12,FFormer Wales and Celtic player John
OL,13,FHartson said: "RIP Leighton James...
OL,14,Fwhat a player, remember watching him
OL,15,Fat the Vetch Field in that great
OL,16,FSwansea team under Tosh... Thoughts
OL,17,Fare with the James family at this sad
OL,18,Ftime."
